### **04-FINDALL** =========================================
###
# Listar todos os livros
GET http://localhost:3002/books
Content-Type: application/json

###
# Listar todos os usuários
GET http://localhost:3002/users
Content-Type: application/json

###
# Listar todos os empréstimos
GET http://localhost:3002/loans
Content-Type: application/json

### **05-FINDONE** =========================================
###
# BOOKS - Sucesso
# @name get_book_success
GET http://localhost:3002/books/{{livro.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json

###
# BOOKS - Falha (404)
GET http://localhost:3002/books/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

###
# USERS - Sucesso
# @name get_user_success
GET http://localhost:3002/users/{{dono.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json

###
# USERS - Falha (404)
GET http://localhost:3002/users/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

###
# LOANS - Sucesso
# @name get_loan_success
GET http://localhost:3002/loans/{{emprestimo_sucesso.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json

###
# LOANS - Falha (404)
GET http://localhost:3002/loans/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

### **06-BUSINESS-RULES** =========================================
###
# TESTE B: Livro já emprestado
POST http://localhost:3002/loans/{{leitor2.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "livroId": "{{livro.response.body.id}}"
}

###
# TESTE C: Dono tenta pegar próprio livro
POST http://localhost:3002/loans/{{dono.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "livroId": "{{livro_do_dono.response.body.id}}"
}

###
# TESTE D: Limite de empréstimos
POST http://localhost:3002/loans/{{leitor2.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "livroId": "{{l4.response.body.id}}"
}
